headline: Military Veterans Can Win Free Travel Franchise From Dream Vacations
summary: Leading travel agency franchise Dream Vacations is recruiting military veterans to enlist in its 14th annual, award-winning "Operation Vetrepreneur: Become Your Own General" contest and is accepting entries from now through September 1, 2025. The number one franchise opportunity for veterans will award three military veterans a free travel agency franchise, continuing a tradition that has given away 64 franchises valued at more than $787,200 dollars since the contest began in 2012.
